# BMI Calculator

This is a simple and modern web-based BMI (Body Mass Index) Calculator. Enter your height (in centimeters) and weight (in kilograms) to instantly calculate your BMI and see which category you fall into.

## Features
- Clean, attractive, and responsive design
- Instant BMI calculation with input validation
- BMI category guide included
- Built with HTML, CSS, and JavaScript

## How to Use
1. Open `index.html` in your web browser.
2. Enter your height in centimeters and weight in kilograms.
3. Click the **Calculate BMI** button.
4. Your BMI and the corresponding weight category will be displayed.

## BMI Categories
- **Underweight:** Less than 18.6
- **Normal weight:** 18.6 – 24.9
- **Overweight:** 25 – 29.9
- **Obesity:** 30 or greater

## Project Structure
- `index.html` – Main HTML file
- `styles.css` – CSS for styling
- `index.js` – JavaScript logic for BMI calculation
- `README` – Project documentation

